TY  - JOUR
TI  - Efficiency of Non-Walrasian Equilibria
AU  - Nayak, P. R.
AB  - [In this paper, Pareto efficiency properties of a non-Walrasian equilibrium for an exchange economy are analyzed. The equilibrium considered is a generalized version of Drèze's equilibrium with price rigidities and rationing.]
